<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Northward" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Northward,</orth> in or to the north: <cit><quote>the fairest creature n. born,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the remnant n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 79</bibl></cit>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>threw many a n. look,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 3, 13</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>